<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Discount Approval Rejected</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 850px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .email-container {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545 0%, #c82333 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        .header::before {
            content: "‚ùå";
            position: absolute;
            left: 30px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .status-banner {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #721c24;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .rejection-summary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffebee 0%, #fce4ec 100%);
            border: 1px solid #f8bbd9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        .rejection-summary::before {
            content: "üö´";
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .rejection-summary h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #c62828;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .opportunity-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .details-header {
            background-color: #6c757d;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .details-grid {
            padding: 20px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        .detail-item {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .detail-item:last-child,
        .detail-item:nth-last-child(2) {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #212529;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .rejected-discount {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #dc3545, #c82333);
            color: white;
            padding: 3px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .decision-details {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .decision-details h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #856404;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .decision-info {
            background-color: white;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .rejection-reason {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .rejection-reason h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #721c24;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .reason-text {
            background-color: white;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 15px;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #424242;
            min-height: 40px;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e3f2fd 0%, #f3e5f5 100%);
            border: 2px solid #2196f3;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .next-steps h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #1565c0;
            font-size: 18px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .steps-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            counter-reset: step-counter;
        }
        .steps-list li {
            counter-increment: step-counter;
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 15px 0 15px 50px;
            position: relative;
            color: #495057;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e3f2fd;
        }
        .steps-list li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .steps-list li::before {
            content: counter(step-counter);
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 15px;
            background: #2196f3;
            color: white;
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .btn {
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff, #0056b3);
            color: white;
        }
        .btn-secondary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c757d, #495057);
            color: white;
        }
        .contact-info {
            background-color: #d1ecf1;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .contact-info a {
            color: #0c5460;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .contact-info a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .signature {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 2px solid #e9ecef;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .highlight-box {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .details-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 10px;
            }
            .action-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            .btn {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 200px;
            }
            .steps-list li {
                padding-left: 40px;
            }
            .steps-list li::before {
                width: 25px;
                height: 25px;
                font-size: 12px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Discount Request Rejected</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="status-banner">
            üö´ Discount approval has been declined - Review feedback and next steps below
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Dear <strong>{!Opportunity.OwnerFullName}</strong>,
            </div>
            
            <div class="rejection-summary">
                <h3>Rejection Notification</h3>
                <p>Your discount request for <strong>{!Opportunity.Name}</strong> has been reviewed and unfortunately <strong>rejected</strong> by your manager. Please review the feedback below and consider the recommended next steps.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="opportunity-details">
                <div class="details-header">
                    üìã Rejected Request Details
                </div>
                <div class="details-grid">
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Opportunity Name</div>
                        <div class="detail-value"><strong>{!Opportunity.Name}</strong></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Account</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{!Opportunity.Account}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Original Amount</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{!Opportunity.Amount}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Requested Discount</div>
                        <div class="detail-value"><span class="rejected-discount">{!Opportunity.Discount_Percent__c}%</span></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Expected Close Date</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{!Opportunity.CloseDate}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Current Stage</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{!Opportunity.StageName}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> Your opportunity is now unlocked and available for editing. Consider the feedback provided and explore alternative approaches to move this deal forward.
            </div>
            
            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>üéØ Recommended Next Steps</h3>
                <ol class="steps-list">
                    <li><strong>Review the rejection feedback carefully</strong> and understand the specific concerns raised by your manager</li>
                    <li><strong>Explore alternative solutions</strong> such as:
                        <ul style="margin-top: 10px;">
                            <li>Adjusting the discount percentage to acceptable levels</li>
                            <li>Offering additional value through services or extended terms</li>
                            <li>Restructuring the deal timeline or payment terms</li>
                            <li>Seeking competitive differentiation instead of price reduction</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Discuss with your manager</strong> to understand what discount level might be acceptable or what additional justification is needed</li>
                    <li><strong>Engage with the customer</strong> to explore win-win alternatives that don't require steep discounts</li>
                    <li><strong>Resubmit if appropriate</strong> with revised terms and stronger business justification</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
            
            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="{!Opportunity.Link}" class="btn btn-primary">üìù Edit Opportunity</a>
                
            </div>
            
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <strong>üí° Pro Tip:</strong> Consider scheduling a brief call with your manager to discuss alternative approaches before making significant changes to your proposal.
            </div>
            
            <div class="signature">
                <p><strong>Best regards,</strong><br>
                Sales Operations Team<br>
                {!Organization.Name}</p>
                
                <p><small><em>Remember: Every rejection is an opportunity to find a better solution. Stay focused on creating value for both the customer and our organization.</em></small></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            This notification was automatically generated by Salesforce on {!TODAY()}<br>
            Opportunity Status: Unlocked and ready for editing | Approval Process: Completed
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>